Stew soup, and BBQ style meat, at a HK style place. Not a very cozy place though.
Good food with reasonable price.  I had afternoon tea with my friend here.  Enjoy it .

This is a long established BBQ meat restaurant, serving also many grassroot Chinese rice & noodle dishes. Price is slightly above other comparable eateries but food quality in general is up a notch also.
Fresh. Tasty. Reasonably priced by HK standards. Large portions.

reviews.text: Nothing special about this place. Reasonable price. Food is good. But witness a quarrel between the wait staffs. Interesting to watch. Probably was a language or choice of words issue
差，吃切鷄飯，鷄不新鲜。其他没吃，下次不會來。
燒鵝肉嫩皮香脆，值得推薦，乾炒牛河也有水準，雞蓉栗米湯勾芡太多
燒味、例湯很靚，小菜也不錯
